&lt;p&gt;Prenuvo is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Client Services Partner&lt;/strong&gt; to support the enhanced scan workflow and ensure a seamless experience for patients and physicians. As a key member of the &lt;strong&gt;clinical team&lt;/strong&gt;, you will be responsible for managing the &lt;strong&gt;end-to-end clinical process&lt;/strong&gt; related to the enhanced scan, coordinating post-scheduling workflows, and assisting with physician education initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
