&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Prenuvo Medical Group and referring practitioners to determine the appropriateness of MRI procedures for patients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate patients about the MRI process, address their questions and concerns, and provide emotional support.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Patient Education and Support:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
