&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance on lifestyle modifications, self-care, and preventive measures.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer emotional support, address patient concerns, and promote overall well-being.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate findings to patients and assist in explaining the implications of the results.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
